cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to solve the problem of aspect-based sentiment analysis. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses various pre-processing steps, features, and methods used, which are common in machine learning and deep learning techniques, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The paper also involves information retrieval techniques to extract relevant information, making cs.IR (Information Retrieval) a possible category. The paper also involves the use of artificial intelligence techniques, making cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) a possible category. Finally, the paper involves the use of neural networks, making cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) a possible category.
